diff -Naurp -X dontdiff linux-cvs/Makefile linux-fixes/Makefile
--- linux-cvs/Makefile	2003-09-12 15:10:36.000000000 +0100
+++ linux-fixes/Makefile	2003-09-22 01:55:31.000000000 +0100
